 to change checkbox size in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"September 18, 2024","description":"Example of change checkbox size in react js with step by step tutorial - aHoisting","social_image":{"absolutePath":"/Users/mac/Documents/hoisting/ahoisting/static/media/template/reactjs.jpg"}}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to change checkbox background color in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-09-19-how-to-change-checkbox-background-color-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to change choose file button text in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-09-17-how-to-change-choose-file-button-text-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2024-09-18-how-to-change-checkbox-size-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2024-09-19-how-to-change-checkbox-background-color-in-react-js/","nextSlug":"/blog/2024-09-17-how-to-change-choose-file-button-text-in-react-js/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2555585279","2714594843","3159585216"]}